+<h2>Attachments</h2>
+
+<p>Endpoints for message attachments with extended metadata.</p>
+
+<h3>Get Message Attachments</h3>
+
+<pre><code>GET /api/attachments?message_id=&lt;message-id&gt;
+Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;
+</code></pre>
+
+<h3>Create Attachment</h3>
+
+<pre><code>POST /api/attachment/create
+Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;
+Content-Type: application/json
+
+{
+  "message_id": "uuid",
+  "file_id": "uuid",
+  "file_name": "string",
+  "file_size": 12345,
+  "content_type": "image/jpeg",
+  "thumbnail_url": "string",
+  "width": 800,
+  "height": 600,
+  "duration": 0,
+  "alt_text": "string",
+  "is_voice_memo": false,
+  "waveform_data": "string",
+  "metadata": "string"
+}
+</code></pre>
+
+<h3>Get Attachment</h3>
+
+<pre><code>GET /api/attachment?id=&lt;attachment-id&gt;
+Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;
+</code></pre>
+
+<h3>Update Attachment</h3>
+
+<pre><code>PUT /api/attachment/update?id=&lt;attachment-id&gt;
